            <q>Page 1, line 20, leave out paragraph (e).</q>
            The noble Lord said: Amendment No. 10 in this series of amendments is concerned with paragraph (e) which states:
            <q>increases in benefits in respect of children under sections 80 and 90 of the <a href="/acts/social-security-contributions-and-benefits-act-1992">Social Security Contributions and Benefits Act 1992</a> (c.4) and sections 80 and 90 of the <a href="/acts/social-security-contributions-and-benefits-northern-ireland-act-1992">Social Security Contributions and Benefits (Northern Ireland) Act 1992</a> (c.7)".</q>
