      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0635P0-02036'>
        <a name='S5LV0635P0_20020516_GCR_158'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-terence-higgins' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S5LV0635P0_20020516_GCR_158' title='Link to this speech by Mr Terence Higgins' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-terence-higgins" title="Mr Terence Higgins">Lord Higgins</a></cite>
          <p class='first-para'>
            I understood that the procedure here, which many of us are not familiar with, was such that we were not supposed to begin a new amendment after 7.30. I may have been misinformed, so I am not going to take responsibility for imposing the rules. We have made considerable progress, so it would seem sensible to adjourn.
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0635P0-02037'>
        <a name='S5LV0635P0_20020516_GCR_159'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/ms-patricia-hollis' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S5LV0635P0_20020516_GCR_159' title='Link to this speech by Ms Patricia Hollis' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/ms-patricia-hollis" title="Ms Patricia Hollis">Baroness Hollis of Heigham</a></cite>
          <p class='first-para'>
            If the noble Lord was misinformed, so was I. I am happy to suggest, if the Committee so wishes, that we reconvene at 3.30 p.m. next Tuesday.
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0635P0-02038'>
        <a name='S5LV0635P0_20020516_GCR_160'>  </a>
        <blockquote class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <cite class='member author entry-title unmatched-member'>The Deputy Chairman of Committees</cite>
          <p class='first-para'>
            The Committee stands adjourned until Tuesday 21st May at 3.30 p.m.</p><p>
            The Committee adjourned at twenty-nine minutes before eight o'clock.
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
